    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133370/extras/702c48b6b67325003916f089db546ae8.avif?t=1751931651\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事背景</h2>可爱的史莱姆公主被大魔王哈本抓走了，为了拯救公主，小史莱姆深入随机变换的地牢深处，与各种魔物发生战斗，最终打败BOSS，在此过程中，一个更大的秘密逐渐浮出水面……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133370/extras/7ccf7852c6aa2d4d0af3c12680e83882.poster.avif?t=1751931651\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133370/extras/7ccf7852c6aa2d4d0af3c12680e83882.webm?t=1751931651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133370/extras/7ccf7852c6aa2d4d0af3c12680e83882.mp4?t=1751931651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><strong>像素风</strong>：精美的像素画风，配合爽快的战斗，感受奇妙的冒险氛围！<br><strong>Roguelike 元素</strong>：每次进入地牢，关卡都会随机生成，敌人和宝箱的位置也会发生变化，让玩家每次体验都充满新鲜感。此外，游戏还拥有永久死亡机制，玩家需要谨慎行动，避免落入陷阱或被敌人击败；<br><strong>丰富的武器和道具</strong>：游戏拥有丰富的武器和道具系统，通过收集和组合，让玩家在地牢探索中更加游刃有余；<br><strong>隐藏内容</strong>：除了丰富的主线战斗外，随机出现的隐藏房间内容也值得探索，这里可是宝箱出现概率最大的地方哦！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133370/extras/5c85373eb2867cb7d97748ef15f48078.poster.avif?t=1751931651\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133370/extras/5c85373eb2867cb7d97748ef15f48078.webm?t=1751931651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133370/extras/5c85373eb2867cb7d97748ef15f48078.mp4?t=1751931651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗技巧</h2>面对远程敌人的发射物，玩家还可以使用弹反攻击，来对敌人进行回击！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133370/extras/5b3294223173a9105f7f617b0f28e290.poster.avif?t=1751931651\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133370/extras/5b3294223173a9105f7f617b0f28e290.webm?t=1751931651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133370/extras/5b3294223173a9105f7f617b0f28e290.mp4?t=1751931651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
